---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Discover">
  <article>
    <header>
      <h1>Discover TLR</h1>
      <p>
        Tiny Leaders: Reborn is a fast, competitive 1v1 Magic format with 50-card 
        singleton decks and a hard 3-mana-value cap. Built from the original 
        Tiny Leaders, TLR delivers tight, interactive games that reward smart 
        deckbuilding and precise play.
      </p>
    </header>

    <hr />

    <section id="nexus">
      <h2>Explore the Format</h2>
      <nav class="discover-grid">
        <article class="nav-card">
          <h3>Rules</h3>
          <p>Master the Rule of 3 and core mechanics.</p>
          <a href="/rules/overview">Read the Rules</a>
        </article>

        <article class="nav-card">
          <h3>Banlist</h3>
          <p>Check the current bans and watchlist.</p>
          <a href="/banlist">View Banlist</a>
        </article>

        <article class="nav-card">
          <h3>Design</h3>
          <p>Deep dives into format philosophy.</p>
          <a href="/design">Design Philosophy</a>
        </article>

        <article class="nav-card">
          <h3>Community</h3>
          <p>Online Leagues, and ways to play in paper.</p>
          <a href="/community">Community Hub</a>
        </article>

        <article class="nav-card">
          <h3>The Feed</h3>
          <p>Latest announcements and articles.</p>
          <a href="/feed">Read Announcements</a>
        </article>

        <article class="nav-card">
          <h3>About</h3>
          <p>Read about our history and meet the Committee.</p>
          <a href="/about">Learn our History</a>
        </article>
      </nav>
    </section>

    <hr />

    <section id="discord">
      <h2>Join the Conversation</h2>
      <p>
        Our Discord is the heartbeat of the community. Join us for:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Competitive brewing & strategy discussions</li>
        <li>LFG (Looking for Game) channels</li>
        <li>Compete in an open year long, online league</li>
        <li>Communicate directly with members of the Tiny Leaders Committee</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        <a href="https://discord.com/invite/jq9KWHAdTm">
          <strong>Join the Official Discord Server</strong>
        </a>
      </p>
    </section>

    <section id="media">
      <h2>Watch & Follow</h2>
      
      <div class="media-block">
        <h3>YouTube</h3>
        <p>
          Watch gameplay, deck techs, and format updates on our 
          official channel.
        </p>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@TinyLeadersRebornCommittee/featured">
            Visit YouTube Channel
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="media-block">
        <h3>Bluesky</h3>
        <p>
          Follow us for quick updates and community highlights.
        </p>
        <a href="https://bsky.app/profile/tinyleadersreborn.bsky.social">
            Follow on Bluesky
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr />

    <aside id="toolkit">
      <h3>Ready to Play?</h3>
      <p>
        Get the tools you need: Cockatrice installation guides, 
        Manabox support, and Moxfield templates.
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href="/community/resources">
          Open the Player Toolkit &rarr;
        </a>
      </p>
    </aside>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Basic styling for the discover cards to maintain structure */
  .discover-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .nav-card {
  /* CHANGED: Use variables so it adapts to Light/Committee themes */
  border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle); 
  background-color: var(--surface);
  
  /* Kept your original spacing */
  padding: 1rem;
  border-radius: 8px;
}

  .media-block {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
</style>